{"tid":2241654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【印度手足rip】印度38歲瘋狂粉絲為偶像禁食4天祈禱　不幸猝死","createTime":"2020-10-13T12:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T14:44:21.000Z","uid":109957,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7031b1bf2fbaa2326729349b3780829dc8af4289","tid":2241654,"uid":109957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:32:45.000Z","msg":"英國《獨立報》報道，印度特倫甘納邦（Telangana）一名38歲男子拉朱（Bussa Krishna Raju）瘋狂崇拜美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump），禁食4天祈求他早日康復，最後竟猝死。根據拉朱家屬描述，他在得知特朗普染疫後，於上周開始禁食為偶像祈禱，卻在11日於親戚家作客喝茶時突然昏倒送醫，宣告不治。<br />\n<br />\n拉朱今年稍早曾因在家中設置約180公分高的「特朗普雕像」而被媒體報道，他安裝雕像後開始進行相關儀式，稱自己住在「特朗普神廟」。他說，他一直為特朗普能順利連任及第一夫人梅拉尼婭的幸福祈禱，還稱自己在安裝雕像前就已經「敬拜」特朗普4年了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8u8oUrw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8u8oUrw.jpg&h=9c1e3d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Op1hYTo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOp1hYTo.jpg&h=fe8889a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特朗普曾在今年2月訪問印度，並在印度總理莫迪（Narendra Modi）家鄉古吉拉特邦（Gujarat）的艾哈邁達巴德（Ahmedabad）和莫迪一同出席「你好，特朗普」集會，拉朱當時曾說希望和特朗普見面，但沒有如願。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VOregEt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOregEt.jpg&h=765c9357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EnglishNEWJ/videos/375566660484028/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEnglishNEWJ%2Fvideos%2F375566660484028%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=d2e7db16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EnglishNEWJ/videos/375566660484028/</a>"},{"pid":"045562066b27b4418f5a105b0b2cb33ecce9f209","tid":2241654,"uid":21141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:34:21.000Z","msg":"癲話連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw rip"},{"pid":"d5a6f558908dbfea57c9cfddfa285982a5af1e5e","tid":2241654,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"..............<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>［20號就截！］德國聯署 終極懶人簽教學］-- 零德文 30秒註冊兼簽埋 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2237125/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2237125/page/1</a><br />\n唔好臨門一腳飛機 ok？<br />\n有12人受緊苦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"dea9af6b0c3089f14c54561e0b39554f694cd09f","tid":2241654,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:35:29.000Z","msg":"希望佢下世 做到美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141fddb0e8a4c0acf24eef14296b249856102426","tid":2241654,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"咁癲"},{"pid":"c4ed8331f388fb94e551b0112be97de72513b13d","tid":2241654,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706445e0422a96d7f47867a6bfb01219c91be7a9","tid":2241654,"uid":66501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:55:52.000Z","msg":"侵侵個樣有浸咖喱味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22769e8e6dfcc12af0ef917932cdc0aa191a011","tid":2241654,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T13:01:19.000Z","msg":"因為trump trump緣故，respect<br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"5cd1c047fec288a89a02a79e2c9851004daa3402","tid":2241654,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T13:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf185b274b9884b4e88abc0e20847aed7cf90c39","tid":2241654,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:44:21